  <title>3A.4 启动 APC 电磁阀和确认托盘升降信号 (2)</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">3A.4 启动 APC 电磁阀和确认托盘升降信号</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">通过该操作，可以在维护模式下打开/关闭 APC 电磁阀。此外，还可以确认末端移动确认信号。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px;"><image src="Actuating APC Solenoid and Signal Confirmation for Pallet UP DOWN.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="32.00%" width="337" height="74" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:5px; line-height:1.50;">制作托盘的操作步骤：</para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">打开维护模式。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11.5pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">­</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text>或<text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">¯</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text>光标键选择托盘提升。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">要打开托盘提升电磁阀，按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">ON</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">要关闭托盘提升电磁阀，按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OFF]</text>软键。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">同样操作托盘上升/CW/CCW 操作。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">指示灯显示如下状态：</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;"><image src="lamp indications.png" scale="30.00%" width="288" height="118" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
  </body>
</topic>
